com.nebukam.easing
Static Public Member Functions | List of all members
Nebukam.Easing.ease Class Reference

Robert Penner's easing. Partial class, normalized methods (t is expected to be in 0-1 range). All easing methods are formatted as like a Lerp would be : from, to, t. More...

Detailed Description

Robert Penner's easing. Partial class, normalized methods (t is expected to be in 0-1 range). All easing methods are formatted as like a Lerp would be : from, to, t.
